ont-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold"> section refers to the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">ability of NHS and social care providers to treat multi-morbidities and the patient as a person rather than focusing on individual conditions</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">2.1. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Of the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">244</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> people who answered the question</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">“</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Do you have any other conditions?</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">”</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">27.9</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">% </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">(</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">68</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> respondents) </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">said no</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36p